title: Freaky Friday: Episode 11
description:
It's the freakiest of Fridays! Happy Friday the 13th to all who celebrate. For this episode, we bring you That Time I Unknowingly Crossed Paths With a Mass Shooter, Be Suspicious of Discount Houses, The Sleepover Disappearance, Your Podcast May Have Saved My Life, Trust Your Instincts, and Signs From My Mom.

If you have an odd but true story, please submit it here.

Click here for information on our tour and to purchase tickets!
